<h3 id="toc4"><span>好康的，是新代码喔</span></h3>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">比代码还刺激</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">来，看这个</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">


<div class="infobox"><div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/stories-in-the-rain">随机作品传送门！</a></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><tt><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carpenter-mark1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3786287); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3786287&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610201436" alt="Carpenter_Mark1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3786287)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carpenter-mark1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3786287); return false;">Carpenter_Mark1</a></span></strong></tt></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">共5篇</p>
<p><br />
<br />
<br />
